    "body": "The gas upper limit of estimation is capped by balance. In your example the account balance is `1` which leads to `fundable=0` upper limit.\r\n\r\nBut I guess your point is why the fee will be automatically set. https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/master/internal/ethapi/api.go#L1399 I think gasPrice is fed by `GasPriceOracle` in this setDefault function.",
